  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/0421464317ca82c9c99f6f41ca9eec2d.avif?t=1712869005\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><strong>Warrior Lords</strong> offers a furious medieval arcade experience, drawing inspiration from classic beat 'em ups. Battle through Western Europe wielding cold steel, delivering powerful kicks and summoning dragons. Choose from 6 unique heroes and defeat your rivals in a quest for supremacy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/da898daa5beabf552c73e763b8575605.poster.avif?t=1712869005\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/da898daa5beabf552c73e763b8575605.webm?t=1712869005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/da898daa5beabf552c73e763b8575605.mp4?t=1712869005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/71f896a4caf618f7855b59b480413dfb.poster.avif?t=1712869005\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/71f896a4caf618f7855b59b480413dfb.webm?t=1712869005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/71f896a4caf618f7855b59b480413dfb.mp4?t=1712869005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/4071d77a191e63e96e00913822f631c4.poster.avif?t=1712869005\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/4071d77a191e63e96e00913822f631c4.webm?t=1712869005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/4071d77a191e63e96e00913822f631c4.mp4?t=1712869005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Arcade Beat 'Em Up Action:</strong> Fight your way through medieval europe in a fast paced arcade brawler.<br></li><li> <strong>Play as one of six unique heroes:</strong> Use special abilities and unique movesets. Summon dragons, fireballs and literal lightning storms to beat your enemies.<br></li><li> <strong>Two Player Local Co-Op:</strong> The game features any-time drop-in co-op. Just press start!<br></li><li> <strong>Customizable Gameplay:</strong> Customize the gamespeed and difficulty to match your style of play.<br></li><li> <strong>Keyboard and Controller support:</strong> Play local multiplayer using the keyboard and controller for both players.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896320/extras/8fda51c73f3b1f1672d599b84fd3137d.avif?t=1712869005\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>One playthrough of the arcade campaign approximately takes 30 - 60 minutes without dying on medium difficulty.</strong>",
